@subsubsection Tilde Underscore: Conditional Newline

Without any modifiers, @t{~_} is the same as @t{(pprint-newline :linear)}.
@t{~@@_}  is the same as @t{(pprint-newline :miser)}.
@t{~:_}  is the same as @t{(pprint-newline :fill)}.
